Class User

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.group12.flus.model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Account
public abstract class User extends Object implements Serializable
The class represents a user of the application. This is an abstract class that provides common properties and methods for all types of users.
